name: Tongits
description: Tongits is a three-player card game that is still in the Rummy family. The objective of the game is to empty your hand cards by forming sets(melds) or minimize the total score when a fight is called or when the central stack is empty. Each player will be dealt 12 cards while the dealer gets 13, and the rest of the cards are left as a draw card. The game begins when the dealer dumps a card. The next person can either pick up the disposed card if that card makes a set or adds to a set they already have or get one from the central stack. Collect hand combinations and dump unnecessary cards. The picking and discarding of cards goes on until someone wins by Tongits, calls a fight, or until the central stack runs out of cards. If this happens, the players tally the points of the cards they have in hand, and the one with the lowest wins. To call a fight, the player needs to put down a meld on the table, and no player drops any card on any of their melds in that round. If the player can use all of their cards in combinations by connecting to opponents’ or the exposed card sets, or if the player gets rid of all their cards, then the player wins by Tongits. Have fun with your friends, enjoy exciting moments, and relieve your stress every day!

To move a ball, just simply click on it to select, then click on the destination square. You can only move a ball to a particular place if there is a path between the current position of the ball and the desired destination. Collect coins as you go and use them to buy new theme colors for the balls. Your main goal is to earn the maximum score and beat the opponent. Points are earned every time you manage to remove balls from the field. The longer the line you make, the more points you will earn.

Are you ready to take on the undead and save the world? Join the adventure now and become the ultimate survivor! Discover new allies so your hero won’t have to face the zombie apocalypse alone! Summon allies to help you in battle and watch as they change in looks and strengths as you progress through the game. Will you choose to fight alongside cowboys, ninjas, gangsters, or other powerful allies? Merge three allies to create a stronger one and unlock even more powerful characters as you reach new milestones. With each new ally, you’ll gain a unique advantage in the fight against the undead.
